headline.print_headline: Italy's New Strike Duo Need to Deliver Against Malta
headline.main: Italy's New Strike Duo Need to Deliver Against Malta

lead_paragraph: Italy’s new strike pairing of Ciro Immobile and Simone Zaza hardly shined against Azerbaijan on Friday but are likely to be given another chance to establish themselves in Monday’s Euro 2016 Group H qualifier in Malta.
